Usage: foreach_in_collection [-help] <var_name> <collection> {<body> }

-help                                   # Prints out the command usage
<var_name>                              # Iterator variable (string, required)
<collection>                            # Collection of objects through which
                                        # to iterate (string, required)
<body>                                  # Script of commands to execute during
                                        # each iteration (string, optional)